main event: A UFO sighting was reported by Pan Am Airlines involving one object observed in flight near Key West, Florida in 1954.
interesting points: The sighting occurred between 0215 and 0232 on February 3, 1954.,The object was observed moving from 30 to 50 feet.,The course of the object was to the northeast.,Multiple possible explanations for the object were concluded, such as a balloon or aircraft.,The observer was a civilian not associated with the flight.
